Package com.assignment.oodpp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectStore
    Object store interface which describes the functionalities of the object store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileObjectStore
    This is the static object store which stores objects in a file.
    InMemoryObjectStore
    This is the dynamic object store which stores objects in memory.
    Main  
    StoreFactory
    This is the factory class which return the relevant ObjectStore when the StoreType is given
    Teacher
    This class is used to test the library by storing objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StoreType
    This enumeration defines the two different object store types InMemoryObjectStore and FileObjectStore
